$interpreted: Hanbei: Hey! Pay attention when you're walking! No pushing!
Ru-yi: Rune, you just kicked me!
Rune: I'm...sorry...
Clark: Shhhh...everyone, be quiet. It's so strange here...
Ru-yi: Wahhhh!!!
Hutchinson: Is that...a spine!? And is that an intestine hanging over there!?
Rune: ...This is fresh blood on this saw...
Hanbei: So that monster back there...
Sophie: Don't-Don't be afraid. It's all so spooky, but it must be fake...right??
Sophie: They're just models...right, Clark?
Clark: ...You really want to hear the truth?
Sophie: ...Eh...
Clark: That odor is coming from an antiseptic. We used to use that at the Academy.
Clark: Even the most deranged scholar of Life Magic couldn't come up with a laboratory as sick as this...
Ru-yi: You-You-You mean this is...a-a-a-alive?
Clark: ...Was alive...
Clark: Everyone, stay on your toes. Whoever the owner of this lab is, they've got absolutely no sense of morality.
Devious: Hsssss...that's the highest compliment anyone's ever given me~
Rune: ...The High Priest, Devious.
Devious: I didn't expect a bunch of worms to crawl into my playroom. Have you come to sacrifice your Soul Energy?
Sophie: You...
Sophie: Sanchez told us what was going on! We're here to save Elio! Where is he?
Devious: Hsss...are you really in the position to save anyone?
Sophie: Rune!
Sophie: Rune, are you okay?
Rune: Sophie...over there...
Sophie: Where?
Sophie: My God...Elio!!
Sophie: *gasp*...it hurts...
Devious: Whatever you think you can do, you can't. I've collected just about all the data I need.
Devious: If anything happens to the lab at this stage of the experiment, I will be very, very angry.
Ru-yi: You...slimy prick.
Clark: Wait. I have something to ask him.
Clark: This experiment...what is it, exactly? The Rune patterns you've inscribed into the New City, that was also your doing, no?
Devious: ...From your expression, I can see that you already know the answer. Let's stop stalling.
Clark: ...Blasted! We're not leaving without Elio. Maria, provide cover!
Maria: Order received,  Master Clark!
Devious: Unrepentant heretics! As you wish!
Sophie: Huff...puff...this time...there's no one here to protect you. Time to pray!
Devious: Hssss...didn't your mother teach you not to speak too soon?
Devious: General, you've seen enough. Show yourself.
Sophie: Wh-Wh-What...?
Rune: ...General Lazer!?
